race.comment: RUSTY ROCKET (8) is progressing well with another good run, placing by half a length (22.84) in a Grade 5 at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Must come into calculations. PAT CARD (5) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing eighth (30.40) in a R/A FIN at Sandown. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Won at his only start from this draw. Great chance to atone. FLETCHER KEEPING (1) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 1.3 lengths back in third (22.77) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Bold showing expected. SAND FIRE (3) won with authority last start. Big chance on that form.
